<i>noun</i>: 폭발 [폭빨], 분출 [분ː출] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>폭발 [폭빨]</dt><br>
<dd>1. outburst</dd><br>
<dd>속에 쌓여 있던 감정 등이 한꺼번에 거세게 쏟아져 나옴.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of a harbored feeling, etc., fiercely bursting out at once.</dd><br>
<dd>2. explosion; spread</dd><br>
<dd>힘이나 열기 등이 갑자기 퍼지거나 일어남.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of power, heat, etc., suddenly spreading or rising.</dd><br>
<dd>3. outbreak</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 사건이 갑자기 벌어짐.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of a certain incident happening suddenly.</dd><br>
<dt>분출 [분ː출]</dt><br>
<dd>1. spurt; jet</dd><br>
<dd>액체나 기체가 세차게 뿜어져 나옴.</dd><br>
<dd>A forceful gush of liquid or gas.</dd><br>
<dd>2. outburst</dd><br>
<dd>쌓였던 감정이 한꺼번에 터져 나옴.</dd><br>
<dd>An unrestrained expression of a deep-rooted emotion.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>